'''''The Rescue''''' ni film documentaire yasohotse 2021 iyobowe kandi ikorwa na Elizabeth Chai Vasarhelyi na Jimmy Chin<ref>The Rescue movie review & film summary (2021) | Roger Ebert <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › the-rescue-mov...</ref> . Bikurikiranye gutabara ubuvumo bwa Tham Luang, ubutumwa bwa 2018 bwakijije [[Umupira w’amaguru|ikipe y'umupira w'amaguru]]  mu buvumo bwamazi<ref>'The Rescue' documentary is not just about cave-diving, but ... <nowiki>https://www.washingtonpost.com</nowiki> › movies › 2021/10/12</ref>. Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 48 rya Telluride ku ya 2 Nzeri 2021, ikaba yarasohotse mu ikinamico muri Amerika ku ya 8 Ukwakira 2021<ref>The Rescue (2021) - Gateway Film Center <nowiki>https://gatewayfilmcenter.org</nowiki> › movies › the-rescue</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Filime ikurikira gutabara ubuvumo bwa Tham Luang <ref>The Rescue | Nat Geo Doc Films <nowiki>https://films.nationalgeographic.com</nowiki> › the-rescue</ref>.

== Umusaruro ==
Muri Werurwe 2019, byatangajwe ko Kevin Macdonald azayobora filime yerekanwe ku gutabara ubuvumo bwa Tham Luang, hamwe na National Geographic Documentary Films igiye gukorwa.  Muri Gashyantare 2021, byatangajwe ko Elizabeth Chai Vasarhelyi na Jimmy Chin bazasimbura Macdonald nk'umuyobozi<ref>The Rescue is an emotionally rousing & suspenseful ... <nowiki>https://www.theaureview.com</nowiki> › watch › the-rescue-is-a...</ref>. 

Abakinnyi ba firime bagize ikibazo cyo kubona uburenganzira ku nkuru, aho National Geographic yashoboye kubona uburenganzira ku nkuru zinyuranye, mu gihe Netflix yari yarabonye uburenganzira ku bunararibonye bw'ikipe y'umupira w'amaguru, ibabuza kuvuga amateka yabo muri filime<ref>The Rescue review – riveting Thai cave rescue documentary <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › film › 2021 › oct › the-...</ref>. 

== Kurekura ==
Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 48 rya Telluride ku ya 2 Nzeri 2021.   Yerekanwe kandi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya 2021 rya Toronto ku ya 12 Nzeri 2021,  aho yatsindiye igihembo cy’abaturage cyo guhitamo inyandiko . <ref>Steve Pond, [https://www.thewrap.com/belfast-wins-toronto-film-festivals-peoples-choice-award/ "‘Belfast’ Wins Toronto Film Festival’s People’s Choice Award"]. </ref>Greenwich Entertainment izakwirakwiza film muri Amerika<ref>National Geographic Documentary Films and Greenwich ... <nowiki>https://www.businesswire.com</nowiki> › 20210903005340 › Na...</ref>.

